OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782820091
OL,3,CHarry Kane makes history in England's
OL,4,Cwin against Panama
OL,6,FEngland Fans celebrate in New York
OL,7,Fafter beating Panama and finishing at
OL,8,Fthe top of Group L, ITV News' Sports
OL,9,FEditor Steve Scott reports
OL,11,FEngland have finished top of their
OL,12,FWorld Cup group after beating Panama 2-
OL,13,F0.
OL,15,FSecond-half goals from captain Harry
OL,16,FKane and Jude Bellingham secured the
OL,17,Fwin for the Three Lions, who had
OL,18,Falready qualified for the knockout
OL,19,Fstages before the match.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
