PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782820091
OL,3,CHarry Kane makes history in England's
OL,4,Cwin against Panama
OL,6,FKane became England's all-time World
OL,7,FCup goalscorer after he headed home
OL,8,FBellingham's cross at the MetLife
OL,9,FStadium in New Jersey to take his
OL,10,Ftally to 11, moving clear of Gary
OL,11,FLineker.
OL,13,FPanama created chances of their own
OL,14,Fand tested goalkeeper Jordan Pickford
OL,15,Fat times, with a goal from Jose
OL,16,FFajardo ruled offside in the second
OL,17,Fhalf.
OL,19,FBut Thomas Tuchel's side were able to
OL,20,Fsee out the result and confirm top
OL,21,Fspot in the group.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782820091
OL,3,CHarry Kane makes history in England's
OL,4,Cwin against Panama
OL,6,FSpeaking after the match, Tuchel said:
OL,7,F"We will step up, the bigger the games
OL,8,Fget, the bigger we will get."
OL,10,FBellingham was full of praise for his
OL,11,Fteammate Kane, telling ITV Sport: "You
OL,12,Fsee the effort that he puts in as a
OL,13,Fcaptain, you see how he leads us, his
OL,14,Fquality speaks for itself - he's the
OL,15,Fbest."
OL,17,FEngland's match against Panama kicked
OL,18,Foff in New Jersey at 10pm UK time,
OL,19,Fwith more than 15,000 England fans in
OL,20,Fattendance.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782820091
OL,3,CHarry Kane makes history in England's
OL,4,Cwin against Panama
OL,6,FHaving gone from the thrill-a-minute
OL,7,Fvictory against Croatia to a dour draw
OL,8,Fwith Ghana, the back-to-back European
OL,9,FChampionship finalists overcame a
OL,10,Fsluggish start to win Saturday's match.
OL,12,FEngland fans react to the win at a
OL,13,Fwatch party in north London
OL,15,FEngland were already guaranteed a
OL,16,Fplace in the knockout phase following
OL,17,FFriday's fixtures and wrapped up top
OL,18,Fspot in Group L with a 2-0 triumph
OL,19,Fthat sets up a last-32 tie against a
OL,20,Fthird-placed side on Wednesday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782820091
OL,3,CHarry Kane makes history in England's
OL,4,Cwin against Panama
OL,6,FEngland will play DR Congo after the
OL,7,FAfrican side sealed their progression
OL,8,Fas one of the best third-placed
OL,9,Ffinishers with a 3-1 in over
OL,10,FUzbekistan in Atlanta.
OL,12,FWhen asked about the possibilities
OL,13,Fbeyond this, the England manager did
OL,14,Fnot want to talk about to far ahead.
OL,16,F"If we get carried away and start
OL,17,Ftalking and thinking about possible
OL,18,Fround of 16, we will just get punished.
OL,20,F"We have a difficult, difficult match
OL,21,Fcoming up in four days", he said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782820091
OL,3,CHarry Kane makes history in England's
OL,4,Cwin against Panama
OL,6,FIt is true that bigger tests are to
OL,7,Ffollow and vast improvements are
OL,8,Frequired if they are to return to
OL,9,FMetLife Stadium for the final on July
OL,10,F19, but Tuchel's men have successfully
OL,11,Fcleared the first hurdle.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Scotland's departure from
OL,14,Fthe 2026 World Cup was confirmed on
OL,15,FSaturday night after Croatia beat
OL,16,FGhana 2-1 in Philadelphia.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
