CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782820091
OL,3,CHarry Kane makes history in England's
OL,4,Cwin against Panama
OL,6,FIf it came down to Group J, Scotland
OL,7,Fwould have needed Austria to beat
OL,8,FAlgeria by two goals, or Algeria to
OL,9,Fwin by four goals but almost
OL,10,Finevitably, it was all academic and
OL,11,Fthe Scots began packing their bags.
